{"tid":2404316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國夫婦相愛77年相繼染疫 病床上情深牽手道別不久雙雙病逝！","createTime":"2021-02-11T15:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T17:11:25.000Z","uid":63113,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"76fb67ddd1fa057ccc71a46992a6c3bc4021d1fb","tid":2404316,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d19c70aeab0e8eeb0cdb779d4ea30a982f9b64c","tid":2404316,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"車喱龜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074eb9610d2f96f1af2d1c4add91bbdaa92e3687","tid":2404316,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"R.I.P"},{"pid":"408dfb93d7bc4dbb41cce2dbfadd314c905b8350","tid":2404316,"uid":63113,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"能與伴侶走到人生盡頭的確不易。英國一對結婚逾70年的九旬老夫婦，早前相繼感染新冠肺炎後離世。二人臨終前能夠團聚，在病床上緊握彼此雙手道別，場面令人感動。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，現年91歲的Derek Firth和太太Margaret，先後因為健康問題住院，其後雙雙感染新冠肺炎，卻被送到不同醫院。有日，他們的女兒Barbara Smith接到醫院電話通知，指媽媽Margaret的情況不樂觀，故詢問他們是否有意前往醫院，Derek趁此機會前往老伴的醫院陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n二人病床上緊握雙手<br />\n<br />\n兩老重聚時，Margaret立即向丈夫問道︰「你之前去哪裡了？」她與丈夫見面後變得格外精神，二人在病床上緊握對方雙手，互相打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjgOWR0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjgOWR0.png&h=4131c09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBarbara透露，爸爸知道可以探望媽媽一定會抓住機會，「他絕對不會不去探望她」，又形容，二人離世前的短暫見面，場面十分悲傷︰<br />\n<br />\n「那是個很悲傷的時刻，他們二人在一起，很優雅，樣子很有愛。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBbWmiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBbWmiS.png&h=180ebc3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDerek和Margaret在14歲開始交往，於1950年結婚，婚後育有5名孩子，後來更是兒孫滿堂。二人一生大部分時間都在帕汀頓 (Partington) 度過。"},{"pid":"671a1ab2b8cb29ba65b66bf49c61d0153beccd22","tid":2404316,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"兩老重聚時，Margaret立即向丈夫問道︰「你之前去哪裡了？」她與丈夫見面後變得格外精神，二人在病床上緊握對方雙手，互相打氣。女兒形容當時媽媽與爸爸見面後，病況似乎有所改善 ; 可惜Derek最終仍在1月31日病逝，而Margaret亦在3日後離世。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2877238/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%EF%B8%B3%E4%B9%9D%E6%97%AC%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E7%9B%B8%E6%84%9B77%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB%20%E7%97%85%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%83%85%E6%B7%B1%E7%89%BD%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8C%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D%20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2877238%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25EF%25B8%25B3%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2597%25AC%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2584%259B77%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2596%25AB%2520%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E7%2589%25BD%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D%2520&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=286910a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2877238/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%EF%B8%B3%E4%B9%9D%E6%97%AC%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E7%9B%B8%E6%84%9B77%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%B8%E7%B9%BC%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB%20%E7%97%85%E5%BA%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%83%85%E6%B7%B1%E7%89%BD%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8C%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D%20</a>"},{"pid":"2635c9e237d5832dc476978987ac51778beff9eb","tid":2404316,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"不能同年同月日生<br />\n<br />\n但願同年同月日死"},{"pid":"6bf85b882f4424ad9a164b6256aca32434a2e961","tid":2404316,"uid":295559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27e11531aa9